Class Answer

java.lang.Object
app.database.util.AbstractModel
app.database.util.AuditModel
app.database.model.Answer
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
@Entity
public class Answer
extends AuditModel
Object-oriented representation for table answers

Storages: Possible user's responses to the question

Logic: When user gets the question he can choose between answers and every of them has impact on the state of variables.
